      <title>抗议者重新集结后，格鲁吉亚警方开始清理街道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/georgian-police-begin-clearing-streets-after-protesters-regroup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚执政党宣布推迟与欧盟就入盟问题进行谈判，引发了连续第二晚的冲突。此后，格鲁吉亚警察和特种部队开始清理第比利斯主要大街上的抗议者和路障。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/georgian-police-begin-clearing-streets-after-protesters-regroup</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 03:41:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁投票决定将非正式采矿许可证延长六个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/peru-votes-to-extend-informal-mining-permits-for-six-more-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁国会周五晚些时候投票决定将一项有争议的许可证延长六个月，该许可证允许非正规矿山在该国经营。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/peru-votes-to-extend-informal-mining-permits-for-six-more-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 02:37:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
