    <item>
      <title>穆迪将巴拿马债务评级展望下调至负面，濒临垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/panama-debt-on-cusp-of-junk-as-moody-s-cuts-outlook-to-negative</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级将巴拿马的信用展望从稳定下调至负面，使其更接近二级垃圾级，因为这个中美洲国家面临财政状况恶化的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/panama-debt-on-cusp-of-junk-as-moody-s-cuts-outlook-to-negative</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 22:24:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪评级将匈牙利信用展望下调至负面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/hungary-s-credit-outlook-cut-to-negative-by-moody-s-ratings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级将匈牙利债务展望从稳定下调至负面，理由是该国治理较弱，有可能失去欧盟的补助金和低成本贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/hungary-s-credit-outlook-cut-to-negative-by-moody-s-ratings</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 21:56:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普维持法国评级 为总理巴尼耶提供缓刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/s-p-sticks-with-france-rating-in-reprieve-for-premier-barnier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于标准普尔全球评级重申对法国债务的评估，法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 在通过预算和继续执政的斗争中获得了短暂的喘息机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/s-p-sticks-with-france-rating-in-reprieve-for-premier-barnier</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 21:55:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行上田表示加息越来越近，工资趋势是关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/boj-s-ueda-tells-nikkei-wage-trends-will-drive-policy-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行行长上田和夫表示，随着通胀和经济趋势按照央行的预测发展，加息“已临近”，这将帮助日元走强，但并未明确支持 12 月份加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/boj-s-ueda-tells-nikkei-wage-trends-will-drive-policy-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 17:45:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西股市因支出计划而遭遇一周亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/brazil-markets-set-for-worst-week-in-two-years-on-spending-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西市场经历了动荡的一周，因为备受吹捧的削减政府支出计划效果远不及预期，加剧了人们对该国预算的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/brazil-markets-set-for-worst-week-in-two-years-on-spending-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 13:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
